Brazil Cuts Tax on Imports of Carbon Steel Plates

-- B y   J e s s i c a   B r i c e
-- 
2011-05-19T13:34:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/brazil-temporarily-cuts-import-tax-on-carbon-steel-slabs.html
(Corrects to say plates instead of slabs in first
paragraph. The story was originally published yesterday.)  Brazil  temporarily cut taxes on
carbon steel plate imports to 2 percent from 12 percent through
Dec. 31, the trade ministry said today in an e-mailed statement.
The tax cut on the heavy plates will apply to imports of up to
30,000 metric tons.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jessica Brice in Sao Paulo at 
 jbrice1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jose Sergio Osse at 
 josse1@bloomberg.net  